{"tid":1370280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727 元朗口號","createTime":"2019-07-27T02:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T03:19:09.000Z","uid":242734,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fde3500f19089be438180008dab2226cbf3874b6","tid":1370280,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:55:06.000Z","msg":"每次遊行成日聽到香港人加油悶悶地，香港人咁有幽默感緊係要整啲新口號，況且附近咁多居民，叫口號可加強文宣<br />\r\n<br />\r\n由於有人屈示威者拆墳，依個口號必須講<br />\r\n1.&nbsp;君堯call 黑打巿民，仲未回水抵拆墳<br />\r\n<br />\r\n要講下遊行目的<br />\r\n2. 保護元朗居民，反對警黑合作<br />\r\n<br />\r\n搞下笑用<br />\r\n3. 提防瘋狗症，白狗亂咬人<br />\r\n<br />\r\n沙田個單未完，元朗yoho 又封商場交通指示<br />\r\n4. 新鴻基,sell Hong Kong&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n有啲人因為悼念啊李鵬所以去元朗<br />\n<code>5. 送64李鵬to the hell</code><br />\r\n<br />\r\n網民係726建議<br />\r\n\t1. 鄉黑牛屎佬 吊你死老母(aa13xx)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n因為元朗太多人投建制派，都要叫下口號講建制派有幾衰，另外港鐵開閘白衫打人都要整個口號，暫時未諗到，依家拋磗引玉，大家幫幫手諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc19ceba64b135b686d74b482245977332cbe15","tid":1370280,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:57:20.000Z","msg":"【小妹文宣出動】多圖  請廣傳  元朗一定要入<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1370271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1370271</a>"},{"pid":"e234932ae45deba7aecced25e19b9cde91334f4d","tid":1370280,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:57:46.000Z","msg":"共產黨  拆祠堂"},{"pid":"adc4bb46af9ef53c5fcf79f0f5ba1acd75f554d2","tid":1370280,"uid":165889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"反警黑勾結<br />\n弘社會正氣"},{"pid":"8ac54e9a5c53d6f94c14688fbd7c18147d1682b0","tid":1370280,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:00:37.000Z","msg":"先撩者賤，打死無怨！"},{"pid":"15678bf6a854f67a312430977ce1d5c65d5564af","tid":137028